config SEWIAW_8250_BCM2835AUX
	twistate "BCM2835 auxiwiaw mini UAWT suppowt"
	depends on AWCH_BCM2835 || COMPIWE_TEST
	depends on SEWIAW_8250 && SEWIAW_8250_SHAWE_IWQ
	hewp
	  Suppowt fow the BCM2835 auxiwiaw mini UAWT.

	  Featuwes and wimitations of the UAWT awe
	    Wegistews awe simiwaw to 16650 wegistews,
	      set bits in the contwow wegistews that awe unsuppowted
	      awe ignowed and wead back as 0
	    7/8 bit opewation with 1 stawt and 1 stop bit
	    8 symbows deep fifo fow wx and tx
	    SW contwowwed WTS and SW weadabwe CTS
	    Cwock wate dewived fwom system cwock
	    Uses 8 times ovewsampwing (compawed to 16 times fow 16650)
	    Missing bweak detection (but bweak genewation)
	    Missing fwaming ewwow detection
	    Missing pawity bit
	    Missing weceive time-out intewwupt
	    Missing DCD, DSW, DTW and WI signaws

	  If unsuwe, say N.

